headline.main: 8 Die in Stampede During Food Handouts in Zambia
headline.print_headline: 8 Die in Stampede During Food Handouts in Zambia

lead_paragraph: Zambian police say eight people have died and 28 have been injured in a stampede during food handouts at a youth center in the capital, Lusaka.
